title: Bali Buddha
typeOfFood: Lacto, Pizza, Indian, International, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant and store. Offers salads, smoothies, samosas (contains butter), pizza, smoothies, non-dairy milk, main dishes using tempeh and tofu, enchiladas, raw platter, pancakes, bagels, hummous. Sells some natural and organic foods products. Has another outlet at Jl. Baniar Anyar 25, A Kerobokan, on way to Cannggu, phone 03618445935.
